'''Hamogoni trees''', native to the planet [[Woteba]], were gigantic, often larger than skyscrapers. They had knee-roots around the size of a [[Dewback/Legends|dewback]], and enormous boughs like great green balconies. They were used as lumber by the [[Saras]] nest of [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] when they occupied the planet. After the end of the [[Dark Nest Crisis]], wood from a hamogoni tree wood be used in a desk in the [[Hapan Embassy]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]].<ref name="inferno">''[[Legacy of the Force: Inferno]]''</ref>

